    dcterms:language "en" ;
    schema:duration "PT16S"^^xsd:duration ;
    cnt:chars "In this lesson, you reviewed some basic inverter operating principles. You were introduced to control objectives used in normal conditions for current, outer loop, reactive power and voltage controls. You also reviewed some control objectives for a fault ride-through response." ;
